VIOLA G. KREINER v. MICHAEL KREINER, SR. [No. 9,

October Term, 1945.]

Decided November 2, 1945.

The cause was submitted to Marbury, C. J., Delaplaine, Collins, Grason, Melvin, Henderson, and Markell, JJ.

Sidney M. Jacobs and H. Harry Rosenberg appeared on brief for the appellant. Joseph Loeffler and Benjamin L. Berman appeared on brief for the appellee. Marbury, C. J.,

delivered the opinion of the Court.
